This is Nitrocid 0.1.0 Service Pack 5 that is a rather small service pack release that brings in several improvements to different kernel areas.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Made `SetCursor*()` functions modifiable
- `[*]` Fixed splash closing
- `[*]` Backported improvements from 0.1.2 for games
- `[*]` Help shows usages in command list

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://gitlab.com/aptivi/main/Nitrocid/-/issues/new).

